data.description: Incredibly well built and cared for home in Jerome that you have to see. This charming and comfortable home is updated through and through, has a newer roof, gas furnace and lots of storage inside and out. The large lot gives you room for days for kids to play, entertaining friends, RV parking and all of your toys. This is a warm 3 bedroom 2 bath home in a great neighborhood and in a great location ready for new owners. You are going to love it.
